C. S. Lee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C._S._Lee 0 Charlie S. Lee (born December 30, 1971), known professionally as C. S. Lee, is a Korean American actor and comedian. He is perhaps best known for playing sex-obsessed forensics analyst Vince Masuka on the Showtime drama series Dexter.
